                "type": "paragraph",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "text": "The scheme \"AGR-61 Agro Service Providers for the Purpose of Making Farming More Profitable With the Help of Farm Mechanization\" introduced by the Agriculture, Farmers Welfare and Cooperation Department, Gujarat, aims to help farmers by providing financial support for farm mechanization through Agro Service Providers, making agriculture more productive and cost-effective."
